<tr><td rowspan="16">aa</td><td class="A">ng</td><td colspan='2'>ngaa1?</td><td><span class='head'>閕</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>張，裂：～嘴</td></tr>
<tr><td>ng/0</td><td>ngaa1</td><td><b>ngaa1<br>aa1</b></td><td><span class='head'>椏</span><span class='sub'><small>丫</small></span></td><td class='mean'>樹木的分枝處</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6" class="B">0</td><td colspan='2'>aa1</td><td><span class='head'>吖</span><span class='sub'><small>啊</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①表示不耐煩地追問：『你講你去唔去～？』；②表示反問：『點會唔得～？』；③表示驚訝或疑問：『你想點～？』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>aa1</td><td><span class='head'>吖</span><span class='sub'><small>啊</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①表讓步同意：『噉又得～』；②表示顯然、反駁：『佢亦都冇話到你乜嘢～！』；③表不以爲然：『呢啲嘢你使乜咁志在～！』；④〔～嘛«maa3»〕表示顯然：『佢日日煅煉～』</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td colspan='2'>aa2</td><td><span class='head'>𦫪</span><span class='sub'><small>啞</small></span></td><td class='mean'>偏灰的，沒有光澤，色澤暗淡：～色</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">3</td><td colspan='2'>aa3</td><td><i><span class='head'>啊</span><span class='sub'><small>阿</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>指示詞，表中遠指，多指非遠非近、手不能及的範圍，這，那：『邇本書系我噶， 嗰本書係你噶，～本書係佢噶，哪本書係乜人噶？』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>aa3</td><td><span class='head'>阿</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>稱呼前綴：～吳公</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>aa3</td><td><span class='head'>啊</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>語氣詞，表肯定、疑問、求證、動作延長等</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">4</td><td rowspan="2" class="A">ng</td><td colspan='2'>ngaa4</td><td><i><span class='head'>𪺾</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>老鷹：～鷹</td></tr>
<tr><td>ngaa4</td><td><b>ngaa4*2</b></td><td><span class='head'>牙</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>牙齒狀的物體，現常特指螺紋：滑～｜唔啱～(比喻物體的兩部分不相互成對，或比喻兩人關係不和、難以相處)</td></tr>
<tr><td class="B">0</td><td colspan='2'>aa4</td><td><span class='head'>呀</span><span class='sub'><small>啊</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①表示要證實某一情況：『張生話佢實嚟～？』｜『係胡小姐～？』；②表示反問，口氣較重：『你估你大晒～？』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">5</td><td class="A">ng</td><td colspan='2'>ngaa5</td><td><span class='head'>瓦</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>泛指陶瓷材質的：缸～｜～缸｜缸～窯</td></tr>
